I '''Manfred von Ardenne''' ([[Eneru 20]], [[1907]] king [[Hamburg]] - [[Mayu 26]], [[1997]] king  [[Dresden]]) metung yang [[Germany|Aleman]] talasalugsug ampong magagamit (applied)[[physicist]] ampong [[talaimbentu]]. Menikua yang mga 600 [[patent]] keng marangle ning [[electron microscopy]], [[medical technology]], [[nuclear technology]], [[plasma physics]], ampong [[radio]] ampong [[television]] technologia.


